<HEADLINE>Five held in drugs swoop</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>1</EDITION>
<PAGE>3</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>974798931</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
--Police and customs officers yesterday seized ecstasy tablets and other drugs
worth an estimated #10m and arrested three people at a motorway service station
near Warrington. Two more men were arrested and a further #1.5m worth of
ecstasy was seized in a follow-up operation.
</TEXT>
